<br>
But watch out. He is one tough mob, and unless you can hit him with a malise, he's going to resist everything you throw at him. <br>
<br>
I used to use earth pet + flame shield, and cast malise/heal till a malise stuck, then nuke away. Half the time I finished him easily with pet at 50% health. The other half I got my a** kicked so badly it was funny. He varies a lot, so now I take the safer route by chain healing (level 8 and level 20 spells alternating). I survive a lot better, though sometimes he gets my pet dangerously low. <p><html>
